summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of all of Lots 50 to 57, inclusive, 61 to 64, inclusive, and 70, Block 65, Replat of the West Seattle Land & Improvement Co.'s Third plat, and Lot 55, Block 447, Seattle Tide Lands, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new section numbered 2-72 and 17-45, respectively.
